<item>
            <title>[SPR-6922] Deprecate SimpleJdbcTemplate in favor of JdbcTemplate</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6922</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;also add &lt;tt&gt;public int[] batchUpdate(String sql, List&amp;lt;Object[]&amp;gt; batchArgs)&lt;/tt&gt; as well as any other methods that exist only on SimpleJdbcTemplate at that time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
